reviewText: just getting my grand daughter into this she loved it as much as my daughter did
Great DVD, but it was just a carbon copy of the first side of the Season 1 disk from the 10th Anniversary Collection.

I picked this up in the hopes it would strike that magical balance of entertaining our toddlers (age 4) and making the parents smile.  And while I found a lot of funny stuff in it it veered too far on the adult side and was often too scary for our girls.

It's a good show and might be worth revisiting at a later date but for now it goes back on the shelf.
